description: This file declares the exported API functions for the Dslh RPC Extension Manager object in the DSL Home Model Implementation. It contains function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing the RPC extension manager, indicating its role as an interface definition for external modules.

methods.name: DslhCreateRpcExtMgr
methods.description: Creates an instance of the RPC Extension Manager with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: DslhRpcExtMgrCreate
methods.description: Creates an RPC Extension Manager instance within a container and owner context.

methods.name: DslhRpcExtMgrRemove
methods.description: Removes an existing RPC Extension Manager instance.

methods.name: DslhRpcExtMgrEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls objects necessary for the RPC Extension Manager's operation.

methods.name: DslhRpcExtMgrInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the RPC Extension Manager instance.
